## TESTING RULES
1. DO NOT fix any code. Test, document, and report only.
2. After EVERY interaction, take a snapshot to verify the result.
3. Screenshot key states (page loads, form submissions, errors).
4. If a page fails to load or a feature is missing, log it and move on.
5. Use the P0-P3 severity system for all bugs found.

## BUG SEVERITY DEFINITIONS
- P0 BLOCKER: App crashes, data loss, cannot proceed at all
- P1 CRITICAL: Core feature broken but workaround exists
- P2 MAJOR: Feature partially works, degraded experience
- P3 MINOR: Cosmetic issues, typos, UI polish

