## TIPS FOR BEST RESULTS

1. **Run one phase per OpenClaw session.** Paste the GLOBAL INSTRUCTIONS
   plus one phase block at a time.

2. **If login fails in Phase 1**, stop and fix auth before running
   other phases. Everything depends on working authentication.

3. **Replace [BASE_URL]** with your actual Replit dev URL in the
   GLOBAL INSTRUCTIONS before pasting.

4. **Save screenshots.** Tell OpenClaw to save screenshots to a
   specific directory if you want to review them later:
   `Save all screenshots to ./traveloure-qa-screenshots/`

5. **For the model setting**, use Claude or Gemini for best browser
   automation results. Add this to your prompt:
   `Always use profile:"openclaw" (isolated browser) for all browser actions`

6. **If a route 404s**, that's useful data — mark it NOT IMPLEMENTED
   and move on. Don't waste time trying to make a missing page work.

7. **Admin credentials**: If you haven't set up a test admin account,
   create one before running Phase 8:
   `admin@traveloure.test / TestPass123!`
   And ensure it has the admin role in the database.
